subSubSection.paragraph:
Based on previous publications (
Mikhailov 1995
, 1998; 
Deeleman-Reinhold 2001
; 
Ono and Hayashi 2009
; 
Huang and Chen 2012
; 
Wu et al. 2015
; 
Yu and Li 2019a
, 
b
; 
Zhang and Yu 2020
), at least 67 

Clubiona

species have been assigned to the 

Clubiona corticalis

group (from rows 1-67 in Table 
3
). A few other known species (from rows 68-73 in Table 
3
) resemble to some species in rows 1-67, but as no one indicated the group placement of these species, they are assigned tentatively to the 

Clubiona corticalis

group in the present paper for the lack of a better solution.
